<p class="sectionheader">
  &#10095; <b>Professional Summary</b>
</p>

<br>

<p class="jobdes">
  Senior Systems Engineer with 15+ years of experience in cloud infrastructure, automation, and DevOps. Proven track record of delivering $200K+ annual cost savings through strategic migrations and infrastructure optimization. Built AI-powered automation systems that reduced helpdesk workload by 80%. Expertise in AWS, Terraform, Ansible, CI/CD, and enterprise-scale migrations.
</p>

<br>
<hr class="line01" />
<br>

<p class="sectionheader">
  &#10095; <b>Key Projects & Achievements</b>
</p>

<br>

<p class="jobpos">
  &#x2022; <b>AI-Powered Ticket Resolution System</b>
</p>
<br>
<p class="jobdes">
  Engineered an intelligent ticketing solution integrating Jira API with Confluence knowledge base. Built AI engine that analyzes 100K+ historical tickets, generates resolution paths with confidence scoring, and auto-responds to tickets above 75% confidence threshold. System handles customer replies, auto-closes resolved tickets or routes to human support. <b>Reduced daily helpdesk ticket volume by 80%.</b>
</p>

<br>

<p class="jobpos">
  &#x2022; <b>Multi-AI Agent Server Documentation Platform</b>
</p>
<br>
<p class="jobdes">
  Architected custom solution to document 600+ legacy servers running 15+ years of undocumented code. Deployed agents across all servers enabling WinRM over custom ports with AWS Security Group restrictions. AI agents scan directories, identify .NET/ASP applications, and auto-generate documentation including code summaries, database connections, and plaintext credential discoveries.
</p>

<br>

<p class="jobpos">
  &#x2022; <b>Citrix VDI to AWS AppStream Migration</b>
</p>
<br>
<p class="jobdes">
  Led first successful migration off 20-year Citrix platform. Migrated 30+ internally built applications serving 2000+ daily users to AWS AppStream. Performed testing, resolved dependency issues, and fixed code compatibility for newer OS platforms. Decommissioned 50+ EOL servers. <b>Reduced yearly licensing and server costs from $145K to $55K (62% savings).</b> Enabled web browser access via SSO, eliminating Citrix client dependencies.
</p>

<br>

<p class="jobpos">
  &#x2022; <b>Enterprise Identity Platform Migration</b>
</p>
<br>
<p class="jobdes">
  Led 5 major migration projects impacting 7000+ users. Migrated email and applications from Office 365 to Google Workspace. Transitioned identity management from AD/Okta to JumpCloud. Migrated 130+ application integrations. Wrote custom automation scripts to map database and server dependencies for migration preparation.
</p>

<br>

<p class="jobpos">
  &#x2022; <b>Server Consolidation & Linux Migration</b>
</p>
<br>
<p class="jobdes">
  Consolidated 120+ EOL servers down to fewer than 40 through strategic migrations and decommissioning. Migrated critical Windows servers to Linux including fileservers, web servers, middleware, reporting services, and AI automation services. <b>Reduced annual EC2 costs from $170K to $70K (59% savings).</b>
</p>

<br>
